# Plan: Render Repost Cards on Feed (matching web app)

## Context
When a user reposts a post, it appears on the feed looking identical to a normal post вҖ” the repost caption, reposter identity, and embedded original post are all missing. The web app (`iskrib_v3`) renders reposts with a distinct layout: a "repost badge" header, the user's quote/caption, and an embedded preview card of the original post. The mobile app has the data (`is_repost`, `repost_caption`, `repost_source` fields on `JournalItem`) but the `PostCard` component ignores them entirely.

## Goal
Make reposted posts on the mobile feed visually match the web app's repost card layout.

